snippet.title: SUPER MARIO Power Star Frenzy - 2016 Legacy Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
YES! You see the title! I'm releasing another demo for Power Star Frenzy due to popular demand on December 9th, 2016! This demo will consist of 60 stars to collect, many levels to explore, and of course the Multiplayer Battle Mode!
Thanks for watching and check out the site guys!

IT HAS BEEN RELEASED! Download it from the site!
►http://www.powerstarfrenzy.com/

SOCIAL MEDIA:
►Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/RandomNICK64
►Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/RandomNICK64
►Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/RandomNICK64
